s.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2444, \"end\": 2452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}, {\"begin\": 2542, \"end\": 2558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2580, \"end\": 2590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Muir\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Muir\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Muir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Muir\"}, {\"begin\": 2616, \"end\": 2641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katarina Johnson-Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In cycling, Tom Pidcock and Bethany Shriever have been name dropped.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Pidcock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Pidcock\"}, {\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bethany Shriever\", \"types\"